org.apache.flex.compiler.codegen.as

Interface IASEmitter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEmitter
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IJSAMDEmitter, IJSEmitter, IJSFlexJSEmitter, IJSGoogEmitter, IJSVF2JSEmitter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ASEmitter, JSAMDEmitter, JSCJSEmitter, JSEmitter, JSFlexJSEmitter, JSGoogEmitter, JSVF2JSEmitter

    public interface IASEmitter
extends IEmitter
    The IASEmitter interface allows abstraction between the IASNodeStrategy and the current output buffer Writer.
    Author:
    Michael Schmalle
